{"tid":1350841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全民黑衣口罩一星期24-31/7-愈係和理非，愈要戴頭盔","createTime":"2019-07-22T13:52:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T09:25:09.000Z","uid":9448,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"6052fa8d755d34d0baa8441f71a0fe2efeba6bcb","tid":1350841,"uid":9448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:52:35.000Z","msg":"代貼 。見到有幾個帖都吹緊24/7開始全民頭盔，想加個<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">全民黑色衣物</span></span>，畢竟呢種和理非活動其實<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">門檻越低越好</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n如果做得成，有六大好處：<br />\n1.顯示我地唔會向專打/拉黑衣人既白色恐佈屈服<br />\n2.<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">培養全民blackbloc 既好習慣</span></span> <br />\n3.保護義士<br />\n4.士氣加持 <br />\n5.國際關注（參考: 警察記者會戴頭盔）<br />\n6.社區黃藍探測器 （如果你個區一個黑色都無，你就知道長輩牆貼得唔夠，要貼上連登一齊去加強文宣）<br />\n<br />\n********<br />\n<br />\n自問自答： 無咁多件黑色衫wo，點解要做七日咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n- 預左第一、二日可能唔係太多人響應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。但係開始左既一直堅持，未開始既後join。去到第七日，可能就真係可以做到成街黑色，甚至成街頭盔。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 黑色衫，每一間衫舖都有，西裝友都有適合你既舖頭。買啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n<br />\n********<br />\n<br />\n覺得可行既，請幫手推一推同廣傳，post一post IG FB，同send一send下面轉發文出去/send俾可以吹大雞既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（張文宣圖整得唔夠靚，希望有覺得可行既巴絲可以幫拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n#黎明前既黑夜係至撚黑暗<br />\n#全民穿黑 #光復香港<br />\n#愈係和理非愈要戴頭盔<br />\n<br />\n****<br />\n<br />\nsend去whatsapp group既轉發文：<br />\n<br />\n【無聲抗議】全民黑衣口罩一星期24-31/7<br />\n<br />\n呢一個星期，希望大家可以盡量著義士既保護衣物上身，愈著得多愈好。<br />\n話俾呢個官商鄉黑既政權知，我地無懼打壓，無懼白色恐佈。<br />\n<br />\n如果工作真係唔允許，希望最少可以著到黑色衣物。<br />\n<br />\n呢個係我地最低限度既無聲抗議，<br />\n亦係對前線既支持同鼓勵。<br />\n<br />\n你既少少堅持，對於前線既意義好大。<br />\n起碼前線一出街就可以知道，佢地唔係孤軍奮戰，只係兄弟爬山緊。<br />\n<br />\n#黎明前既黑夜係至黑暗<br />\n#全民穿黑 #光復香港<br />\n#愈係和理非愈要戴頭盔<br />\n<br />\n****<br />\n文宣圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4o6ATZJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4o6ATZJ.png&h=b0d61e36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相關活動文宣圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/drLep54.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdrLep54.png&h=e078e8b2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aMUbsjp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaMUbsjp.png&h=17538598&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/22/214953_643783061fc11204419e56a9c1822c69.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F22%2F214953_643783061fc11204419e56a9c1822c69.png&h=cc6fec16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n****<br />\n<br />\n相關貼文<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>全民頭盔月<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1343516\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1343516</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n24/7 全民頭盔 無聲抗議運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1347087\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1347087</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n暫24號: 先推一日做全民頭盔日 以保港鐵乘客 及行街市民安全<br />\n之後: 令個社會關注，長時期全民戴頭盔搭港鐵戴頭盔出街；有能力既，可以係港鐵站派頭盔比乘客。 <br />\n<br />\n目的: 保障全港市民安全 以及 令克警無理由充公我地頭盔物資 + 合理化拎頭盔出街 綠卡都唔駛考<br />\n<br />\n合法攜帶防身武器 你問我答(討論)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1344249\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1344249</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n全民 BLACK BLOCK<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1203119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1203119</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</blockquote>"},{"pid":"29f29c176d6a9d9e4c8a0a0ff0cf284ee66719eb","tid":1350841,"uid":9448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:52:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2179b6dddf5dabe0ac4782bb6cd5b5b50b89d68b","tid":1350841,"uid":9448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:57:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19b61e120ebc1853353c6b2848f8f39b3d94a441","tid":1350841,"uid":273252,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:09:23.000Z","msg":"同意你個plan<br />\n我果邊算係推起左啲<br />\n不如集中post係我果邊<br />\n<br />\n全民頭盔月<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dnomPS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dnomPS</a>"},{"pid":"e903b5ee5af220ed7dd49d2465d2ebd4e815c787","tid":1350841,"uid":37029,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:15:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而家竟然搞到著黑衫出街都要有心理準備<br />\n支持香港人集體無聲抗議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f55d6a11d43e0fe11d293a51e1c114f8b3f805","tid":1350841,"uid":137265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:07:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"462eea7c2a7f141d81b68ca0a857bfa53c7bc67c","tid":1350841,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:32:52.000Z","msg":"推到多d人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b85c1919b93a45ce5069c484566c5072082b4b74","tid":1350841,"uid":82152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r